<p>Note that this hyperbola has no <em>y</em>-intercept because if <em>x</em> = 0, then −<em>y</em><sup>2</sup> = <em>b</em><sup>2</sup> which is not possible. The hyperbola is symmetric with respect to both <em>x</em>-and <em>y</em>- axes.</p>
